1
00:00:15,133 --> 00:00:17,566
Hey. So many things in hands.

2
00:00:17,566 --> 00:00:18,886
Where are you going to take them?

3
00:00:25,166 --> 00:00:26,166
Did you not hear?

4
00:00:26,666 --> 00:00:29,400
I'm asking who would you
take all these stuffs to.

5
00:00:32,366 --> 00:00:33,366
They're for Tee.

6
00:00:34,133 --> 00:00:35,133
Tee?

7
00:00:37,800 --> 00:00:39,166
That sweet looking guy?

8
00:00:40,133 --> 00:00:42,133
What a shame.
That person could have been me.

9
00:00:44,300 --> 00:00:45,833
Why does it have to be you?

10
00:00:46,666 --> 00:00:47,699
Even if it's you.

11
00:00:48,233 --> 00:00:49,633
I ain't gonna carry things for you.

12
00:00:50,433 --> 00:00:51,300
Please move out of the way.

13
00:00:51,300 --> 00:00:52,233
I'm in a hurry.

14
00:00:52,300 --> 00:00:53,300
Wait.

15
00:00:54,400 --> 00:00:55,800
Could you help me check my bicycle?

16
00:00:56,433 --> 00:00:58,793
There's noise coming out of the bicycle
all the way up here.

17
00:01:23,099 --> 00:01:24,433
What is the issue?

18
00:01:24,866 --> 00:01:26,626
I don't see anything wrong
with the bicycle.

19
00:01:27,266 --> 00:01:28,933
Stop fooling around.

20
00:01:30,099 --> 00:01:31,300
I'm going back to Tee.

21
00:01:31,300 --> 00:01:34,133
One word, Tee. Another word, also Tee.

22
00:01:35,233 --> 00:01:37,699
Let me try once and I'll never forget.

23
00:01:42,099 --> 00:01:43,233
Let me go now.

24
00:01:43,766 --> 00:01:44,966
If you don't want any problem.

25
00:01:47,433 --> 00:01:48,433
Fine.

26
00:01:48,933 --> 00:01:50,266
I'll let you go this time.

27
00:01:51,433 --> 00:01:52,433
Next time,

28
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,520
Who will be the one
that won't let go?
